<specimenCount box="[498,520,610,633]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,679,814]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">
This genus is widely spread in the Old World (63 species in the Palaearctic, 
<quantity box="[1005,1076,679,706]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.667" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" unit="in" value="105.0">105 in</quantity>
the Afrotropical, and five in the Oriental regions) (
<bibRefCitation author="Pagliano, G. &amp; Brothers, D. J. &amp; Cambra, R. &amp; Lelej, A. S. &amp; Lo Cascio, P. &amp; Matteini Palmerini, M. &amp; Scaramozzino, P. L. &amp; Williams, K. A. &amp; Romano, M." box="[361,599,715,742]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" pagination="5 - 425" refId="ref19407" refString="Pagliano, G., Brothers, D. J., Cambra, R., Lelej, A. S., Lo Cascio, P., Matteini Palmerini, M., Scaramozzino, P. L., Williams, K. A. &amp; Romano, M. (2020 [&quot; 2018 &quot;]) Checklist of names in Mutillidae (Hymenoptera), with illustrations of selected species. Bollettino del Museo Regionale di Scienze Naturali di Torino, 36 (1 - 2), 5 - 425." type="journal article" year="2020">
Pagliano 
<emphasis box="[470,529,715,741]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">et al.</emphasis>
2020
</bibRefCitation>
). Currently eight species of this genus are known from 
<collectingCountry box="[1241,1367,715,741]" name="Azerbaijan" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Azerbaijan</collectingCountry>
, three of these species are newly recorded from this country. The species 
<taxonomicName authority="Skorikov, 1935" authorityName="Skorikov" authorityYear="1935" box="[909,1247,751,778]" class="Insecta" family="Mutillidae" genus="Dasylabris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paupertina">
<emphasis box="[909,1068,752,777]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">D. paupertina</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Skorikov, A. S." box="[1075,1247,751,778]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" pagination="257 - 349" refId="ref20282" refString="Skorikov, A. S. (1935) Zur Mutilliden-Fauna Zentralasiens. Trudy Tadzhikskoi Basy Akademii Nauk SSSR, 5, 257 - 349, 7 pls. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1935">Skorikov, 1935</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Skorikov, 1935" authorityName="Skorikov" authorityYear="1935" class="Insecta" family="Mutillidae" genus="Dasylabris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gobicola">
<emphasis box="[1303,1436,751,777]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">D. gobicola</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Skorikov, A. S." box="[151,322,787,814]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" pagination="257 - 349" refId="ref20282" refString="Skorikov, A. S. (1935) Zur Mutilliden-Fauna Zentralasiens. Trudy Tadzhikskoi Basy Akademii Nauk SSSR, 5, 257 - 349, 7 pls. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="1935">Skorikov, 1935</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
are excluded from the list of 
<collectingCountry box="[651,774,787,813]" name="Azerbaijan" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">Azerbaijan</collectingCountry>
fauna as wrongly recorded.
</paragraph>
